research/history/logs/agent_action_0295.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"扩展兼容新结构 probe：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 的最终重构为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r1(x))} α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r2(x))} α_{e,m} b_{e,m} + Σ_{u∈S_res(r3(x))} γ_u c_u，其中 r1/r2/r3 是逐级 residual。两层 shared residual coarse stage、PK-routed expert cleanup 与最后的 tiny global residual cleanup 都只访问静态向量库并做有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在 r294 已显出较好 exceed 的 dual-shared PK scaffold 上再加一个很小的全局 residual tail-cleanup，能比现有 dual-shared PK 更强地压住 hard-token exceed。","summary":"已实际新增并集成 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，只修改 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。该 family 是对 r294 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的结构升级：保留双 shared coarse + PK cleanup，只再追加一个 tiny factorized residual cleanup。按本地 exact-string smoke 与 cost 估计，在继承 r294 的 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 配置下 total_cost_ratio 约 `0.13x`，仍在当前目标带内；因此本轮是一次 matched-cost 附近、明确面向降低 exceed 的 scaffold-upgrade probe。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险很直接：`cost≈0.13x` 已经要求 exceed 至少接近 `0.09~0.10` 才有机会逼近阶段目标，交换率门槛很高。如果这轮 exceed 只是比 r294 小幅下降几个点，仍不够支撑主线；但它是当前最贴近 winning scaffold 的高信息增量升级之一，值得用一轮回答。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"],"notes_to_memory":["已落盘新增 family：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual`，完成了 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch/class 接线。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_residual` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=2048, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计：selection_ratio≈0.09，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.13；处于当前允许的 matched-objective 探索带。","该 family 的结构语义是：dual shared residual coarse stage 吃主干，PK experts 做中层 cleanup，tiny factorized residual head 做尾部 cleanup；与 r294 相比，信息增量集中在 hard-token tail-cleanup 机制。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮 exceed 明显低于 r294 且 objective 改善，再以该 family 为 anchor 做一次极小幅 knee 校准，例如 `STAGE1_RATIO`。","若本轮 objective 仍无改善，则说明在 dual-shared PK scaffold 上追加 tiny global residual cleanup 的交换率不足，后续应停止继续叠加同类 cleanup 层。","若本轮出现 sanity 或 registration 异常，优先按 exact architecture string 回查 config whitelist / dispatch / class reachable 性，而不要把问题误判成训练质量结论。"],"reference_round":294}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0276.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s^{k1}(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh}(x) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^{τ,k2}(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 {B_s^sh} 是两个 always-on shared 静态子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}(x)b_{s,i}^{sh}，E_pk^*(·) 表示在 residual 上由 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + residual 上的 PK 路由 + 少量 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r275 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，在 exact 同成本 `total_cost_ratio=0.109375` 下引入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup path，能比固定 AE=2 的 dual-shared scaffold 更有效地处理 hard tokens，把 exceed_alpha_0.50 继续从 r275 的 `0.172059` 往下压，并争取逼近或击败 incumbent r266。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在同成本下明显优于 r275，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试在 adaptive cleanup 存在时是否重新回到更轻 coarse split 更优。","如果该 family 只比 r275 小幅更好但仍明显不够接近 incumbent，则记录为“variable-active path 有帮助，但不足以带来 regime shift”，后续应停止在 adaptive 邻域细扫。","如果该 family 不如 r275，则说明在当前 PK/shared scaffold 上 adaptive 1-or-2 expert path 不是主要突破口，后续应转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义或 coarse 表达方式的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支仍保持双 shared banks，但 routed cleanup 从固定 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 改为按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个 PK experts；与 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 容量从 1 个 shared bank 扩到 2 个。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=294912 (`0.0703125x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=458752 (`0.109375x`)；与 r274/r275 的 dual-shared fixed-AE scaffold 同档，因此这是一个干净的 matched architecture probe。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 14 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","当前 dual-shared scaffold 已给出真实正向证据：r275 相对 r274 在同成本下把 exceed 从 `0.177462` 压到 `0.172059`，说明这条新 scaffold 仍值得一次 architecture-level upgrade，而不是继续做 split 邻域细扫。"],"reference_round":275,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段约束。最近两轮 r274-r275 都停留在同一 dual-shared family 内，且 objective 仍未接近 incumbent；按策略此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续补 `STAGE1_RATIO` 近邻点。选择 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续在 dual-shared 上做 `0.125/0.375` 分裂点，是因为它直接测试当前高优先级方向“variable-active path by difficulty”，同时完全建立在已有 winning scaffold 的近同成本升级上。代码侧仅新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增 tunable key，因此不需要改 `config_resolution`、`runner` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。主要风险是 adaptive active 在单-shared 版本上曾给过弱负信号；但 dual-shared scaffold 已把 coarse 主干抬强，当前最有价值的问题正是这是否能让 difficulty-aware cleanup 真正发挥作用。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r275 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚 shared coarse 主干 + 按难度可变 1-or-2 PK cleanup path”能否在与 dual-shared fixed-AE 完全同成本的 `0.109375x` 档位继续显著压低 exceed。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
