research/history/logs/agent_round_0291.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"直接兼容 probe：`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的最终重构可写为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^{sh} b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk^*(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}，其中两路 always-on shared 静态子库先吸收 coarse 主干，随后 product-key router 按 token 难度自适应启用 1 或 2 个静态 expert 子库做 JumpReLU cleanup。该形式仍能直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态子库查表 + 加权求和推理链路，因此兼容性判定为直接兼容。主假设是：在 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 stronger coarse scaffold 上接入 difficulty-aware variable-active cleanup，可能比已测试的单 shared adaptive 版本更能压低 hard-token exceed。","summary":"从 r279 做单变量 architecture switch 到 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。这不是回到低信息细扫，而是沿当前最相关的 shared+PK scaffold 测试“更厚 shared coarse + variable-active residual cleanup”这一结构升级。按本地烟测与 cost 估计，`NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 下 total_cost_ratio 约 `0.11x`，处于 matched-objective 带；若该 family 不能在近同成本下明显降低 exceed，就可以把这条 variable-active dual-shared 支线一并降级。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"风险在于 `shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 先前已给过负信号，而且当前 cost proxy 对 adaptive path 的计费与 dual_shared PK 基本相同，因此这轮几乎完全是在赌 exceed 改善。如果 exceed 仍停留在 `~0.16+`，这条线就不值得继续主导预算。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 下可实例化并 forward/backward。","本地 cost 估计（以 r279 配置为 anchor）：selection_ratio≈0.07，deployment_ratio≈0.04，total_cost_ratio≈0.11，与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 同量级。","`dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 尚未在当前 target 上得到真实 objective 证据；本轮的价值在于回答 variable-active cleanup 接到 dual shared scaffold 上是否值得继续。"],"next_hypotheses":["若本轮在近同成本下把 exceed 明显压到 `<=0.15` 一带，再以本 family 为 anchor 单变量检查 `NUM_EXPERTS 1024→2048` 是否能继续放缓 hard-token exceed。","若本轮 objective 仍不优于 incumbent，说明现有 adaptive-active 语义不足以改善 low-K tradeoff，后续应转向真正新的 cleanup 机制，而不是继续扫 adaptive path 邻域。","若本轮出现运行异常或配置不符，优先核对 round config / checkpoint config 中 architecture 是否确实写成 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，不要把无效轮次当结构证据。"],"reference_round":279}
