research/history/logs/agent_round_0278.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(h(x))} α_{s,i}^{sh}(h(x)) b_{s,i}^{sh} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是低秩 shared bottleneck，{b_{s,i}^{sh}} 是两个静态 shared coarse 子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_sΣ_i α_{s,i}^{sh}b_{s,i}^{sh}，{B_e} 是静态 PK-routed expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 low-rank hidden 上的 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 experts，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r263 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用极轻的 dual low-rank shared coarse branch 替代 plain PK 的无主干设置，同时保留 full-expert PK cleanup，能够在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.082427978515625` 的近同成本档位比 r277 的 single-shared lowrank 变体显著更稳住 exceed，并争取在保持低成本的同时压低 exceed_alpha_0.50 到 `0.19357784271240236` 以下以击败 r263。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.08243x` 下明显优于 r263，并接近或击败 r266，则下一轮应留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125`，测试更轻 shared split 是否能进一步提升 low-cost objective。","如果该 family 只比 r277 好、但仍明显输给 plain PK 或 incumbent，则记录为“dual low-rank shared coarse 修复了 single-shared lowrank 的容量不足，但 lowrank shared family 仍不够强”，后续不要继续在这条线做低信息细扫。","如果该 family 仍明显失败，则可更果断地下调“lowrank shared coarse + PK cleanup”整条方向优先级，把预算转向其他真正改变 cleanup 语义的新结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：low-rank shared coarse 子库从 1 个扩到 2 个；与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：shared coarse 分支改为 low-rank bottleneck 上的 factorized heads，而 routed cleanup 仍保留 full-expert PK JumpReLU encoders。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","实现中继续将实际 shared hidden 维度限制为 `min(FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT)`；在当前 recipe 下实际 hidden_dim=56，因此新增第二个 shared lowrank head 的成本很低。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=181888 (`0.043365478515625x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=345728 (`0.082427978515625x`)；这比 r277 的 single-shared lowrank 变体仅高 `0.0007476806640625x`，但 shared coarse 容量翻倍。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 16 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","r277 已给出强负信号：`shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在 `0.081680x` 下 exceed 达到 `0.223148`，说明 single-shared lowrank coarse 明显容量不足；本轮新 family 正是最小成本地测试这个结论是否能通过双 shared heads 被修复。"],"reference_round":263,"self_review":"这轮符合当前阶段优先级。r274-r277 已连续探索了 dual-shared、adaptive、single-shared-lowrank 三个不同槽位，其中只有 dual-shared 给出一定正向 exceed 信号，而最新 r277 证明“single lowrank shared coarse + PK cleanup”虽然极便宜，但 exceed 崩得太厉害。选择 `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的理由不是继续做邻域插值，而是用一个最小新结构直接回答 r277 暴露出的核心问题：失败是来自 lowrank shared 表达本身，还是来自 shared coarse 容量太薄。相对 r263 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，满足单变量规则；代码侧只新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke。主要风险是即便 shared coarse 翻倍，lowrank shared 表达仍可能不够，导致 exceed 仍远高于 target；但这轮会以很低的额外成本给出一个高信息量结论。","summary":"已新增并接通 `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r263 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 做一轮 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“更厚的 low-rank shared coarse + full-expert PK cleanup”能否在 `0.08243x` 的低成本档位修复 r277 的 exceed 崩塌。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
