research/history/logs/agent_round_0280.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式写为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1}(x) b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1(x))} α_j^{sh,2}(x) b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} γ_{e,m}(x) c_{e,m}，其中 r_1(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1}，r_2(x)=r_1(x)-Σ_j α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2}。两路 shared bank 与 routed PK expert 子库都仍是静态库；在线链路只是“shared bank 1 查表 -> residual -> shared bank 2 查表 -> residual -> product-key 路由到静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 JumpReLU sparse support -> 查表加权求和”，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态子库有限加权和推理链路，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` 等不兼容 family 仍只作历史参考，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。本轮唯一主假设是：r275→r279 在同一 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` family 内只把 objective 从约 0.2814 小幅压到约 0.2806，说明并行 dual-shared 的 split 轴已接近平台；下一步更值得回答的不是继续补近邻 `STAGE1_RATIO`，而是把两个 shared bank 从“同一 shared stage 内并行竞争 top-k”改成“两个 residual shared stage 串联清理主干”。相对 r279 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到新实现的 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=1024, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56, STAGE1_RATIO=0.375, adam, LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，是当前同成本 0.109375x 下信息增量最高的新结构 probe。它与现有 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：旧 family 在两路 shared bank 上做一次联合 shared top-k；新 family 则先用第一个 shared bank 做 coarse reconstruction，再让第二个 shared bank 只在 residual 上工作，目标是在不增加 active path 和不增加成本的前提下，更好地降低 hard-token tail。若该串联 residual shared 语义能把 exceed 从 r279 的 0.171186 再压约 0.0056 到 <=0.1656，就有机会在同成本下反超当前 incumbent 0.275001。","summary":"已落盘并自检新的 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`。建议以 r279 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，做一轮与 dual-shared scaffold 同成本的 matched architecture probe，直接裁决“串联 residual shared coarse + PK cleanup”是否比现有并行 dual-shared 更能压低 exceed。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮代码改动和实验设计都满足约束。代码侧我只做了最小新 family 接入：`sparsify/config.py` whitelist、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch+实现、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` allowlist、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md` compatibility 行；没有新增 tunable env key，因此不需要改 `controller.py`、`config_resolution.py`、`runner.py` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。实验侧相对 r279 仍只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以现在值得开新 family，而不是继续扫 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或回到 low-rank/variable-active 线，是因为 r279 只给出很小的同 family 改善，且 r276/r277/r278 已分别对 adaptive-active 与 low-rank shared 给出负信号。主要风险是这个新 family 虽然保持 exact 同成本，但串联 shared residual 可能只改善均值误差而不改善 exceed；如果结果如此，就可以更果断地结束 dual-shared 邻域的继续打磨。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 的精确结构差异是：`dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 在两路 shared bank 上做一次联合 shared top-k；新 family 改为 shared bank 1 先重构、shared bank 2 只在 residual 上继续工作，然后再做 PK expert cleanup。","本地 exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56, stage1_ratio=0.375, factorized_hidden_dim=256, trunk_rank=16)` 在 CUDA 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地成本复核已通过：`selection_cost_estimate(n_output=4096)` 给出 selection_accesses=294912、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=458752、exact combined_ratio=0.109375，与 `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 同成本且低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表。","兼容性表已补充：`residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 属直接兼容 family；当前 objective leaderboard 仍只应比较兼容 family。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在同样 0.109375x cost 下把 exceed 压到约 0.166 附近并刷新 incumbent，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 或 `0.5`，定位串联 shared residual 的最佳 coarse/cleanup 分工。","如果该点明显优于 r279 但仍未赢 incumbent，则记录为“串联 residual shared 语义优于并行 dual-shared”，后续优先在这个新 scaffold 上探索更强 cleanup 升级，而不是再回 dual-shared 旧 split 轴。","如果该点与 r279 基本持平或更差，则可把 dual-shared 邻域整体视为已接近平台，下一轮应切到完全不同的结构槽位，而不是继续扫 shared split 或 shared ordering。"],"reference_round":279}
