research/history/logs/agent_round_0158.stdout.log:551:shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert {"status": "discarded", "design_hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。", "tested_configs": [{"round": 144, "stage": "prototype", "k": "112", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.13998684287071228", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 156, "stage": "prototype", "k": "96", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.14623424410820007", "run_health": "normal"}], "known_issues": [], "next_steps": ["如果该点在约 0.28x 下明显优于 r155 且接近当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，定位 coarse stage 与 residual expert 的分工边界。", "如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则可把 shared-lowrank 两段式方向在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，下一轮转向更中成本但更有希望形成新段的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` matched probe。", "如果该点仅小幅优于 r155 但仍不进入非支配前沿，则记录为 shared-lowrank coarse 比 shared-lowrank routed 更稳，但仍不足以替代现有 low-cost anchors，后续不要继续在该 family 上做连续局部微调。"], "best_fvu": null, "last_round": 156}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0158.stdout.log:552:shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk {"status": "discarded", "design_hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 router 选少量 experts + shared lookup + expert-local top-k lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前最高优先级的 hetero-MoE 结构“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head / local top-k”在约 0.28x total_cost 下，是否能优于现有 0.28x-0.32x 低成本 frontier 段。", "tested_configs": [{"round": 129, "stage": "prototype", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.1219072937965393", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 130, "stage": "stabilize", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.2266390025615692", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 134, "stage": "mainline", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.12481768429279327", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 135, "stage": "mainline", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.13039079308509827", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 141, "stage": "mainline", "k": "112", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.14034616947174072", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 155, "stage": "prototype", "k": "96", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.14630839228630066", "run_health": "normal"}], "known_issues": [], "next_steps": ["如果该点在约 0.28x 下接近或优于当前 0.28x-0.32x anchors，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，测试 shared scorer 还能否继续左移而不明显掉质。", "如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则不要继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做局部扫参，下一轮切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 做同 recipe 的 matched architecture probe。", "如果结果异常差且与历史 r141 同向，可把“shared low-rank basis + routed local head”在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，转回别的未充分验证结构槽位。"], "best_fvu": null, "last_round": 155}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0240.stdout.log:1547:research/history/round_summaries/round_0178.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然该点略高于 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近三轮已经连续排除了 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，当前最需要的是用一个仍在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内的高优先级结构槽位，把“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”这条线做一次更干净的 matched validation。选择它而不是继续回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，是因为前者已有更强负信号，后者又属于当前已明确下调优先级的 two-stage/hetero residual 方向。主要风险是该 family 在 r172/r174 已有偏弱结果；但这次是以当前更相关的 r165 low-cost anchor recipe 做 fresh matched probe，结论会更直接。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0240.stdout.log:1548:research/history/round_summaries/round_0178.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然该点略高于 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近三轮已经连续排除了 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，当前最需要的是用一个仍在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内的高优先级结构槽位，把“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”这条线做一次更干净的 matched validation。选择它而不是继续回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，是因为前者已有更强负信号，后者又属于当前已明确下调优先级的 two-stage/hetero residual 方向。主要风险是该 family 在 r172/r174 已有偏弱结果；但这次是以当前更相关的 r165 low-cost anchor recipe 做 fresh matched probe，结论会更直接。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0240.stdout.log:1713:research/history/round_summaries/round_0187.json:38:      "r182-r186 已连续给出 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`、`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_factorized_residual` 的低成本负信号；当前不应继续让这些 family 主导 `<0.25x` 预算。"
research/history/logs/agent_round_0240.stdout.log:1845:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
