PERT=56` 让 exceed 明显回弹、objective 不再下降，则说明当前 PK 主线在 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` 下的最小可用 local width 更接近 80；后续应停止继续扫 width，转而优先选择能明确解释 small-K exceed 更慢退化的新结构槽位。"],"reference_round":262}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0262.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式继续写为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E_pk(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e^τ(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 {b_{e,i}} 是静态 expert 子库原子，E_pk(x) 由两路 product-key router 给出少量 active experts，S_e^τ(x) 由 expert 内 JumpReLU 形成局部稀疏支持。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“left/right product-key 打分 -> 选择少量静态 expert 子库 -> expert 内 sparse support -> 查表加权和 -> 选择性在线补偿”，不涉及动态字典生成，因此 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 仍判定为直接兼容。带 shared/trunk 的 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 等 family 只属于扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk`、`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` 等 sample/batch-coupled family 仍是不兼容，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。r261 已把真实 compatible frontier 刷到 controller objective≈0.283066 = cost 0.10x + exceed 0.183066，exact round-summary objective=0.284628 = exact cost 0.1015625 + exceed 0.183066，且训练曲线 `curve_still_improving=true`，说明当前主线仍有高价值未验证假设，不需要立刻切新结构槽位。当前最干净的问题是：在 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` 已确认有价值后，micro-expert width 是否还能继续左移。相对 r261，本轮只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 96 降到 80，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`、`K=32`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，直接测试当前 PK 主线的 width knee 是否还低于 96。按本地 exact 成本复核，`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80` 时 selection_accesses=229376、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=393216、exact total_cost_ratio=0.09375；controller 两位小数口径下为 0.09x。若要刷新 controller frontier，只需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1930657422542572`；若要同时刷新 r261 的 exact objective，则需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1908785`。这说明 `96 -> 80` 是一档胜面很现实、且归因非常干净的主线宽度 probe。","summary":"建议以 r261 为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80`。r261 已证明更大 compositional bank 值得保留；现在最有信息量的单变量问题不再是继续堆 bank，而是确认 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` 下的真正 width knee。`80` 是第一档能把 controller 成本从 0.10x 压到 0.09x、同时又明显比 `64/72` 更稳健的宽度 probe。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮继续留在同一 family 有充分依据。r261 刚刚把 compatible frontier 从 r251 的约 0.2935 降到约 0.2831，属于明确改进；而且曲线仍在改善，因此当前 family 还存在一个高价值、未验证、且足以改变后续搜索方向的主问题：在 1024-bank 条件下，96 是否仍偏宽。相对 r261 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，归因比改 `K` 或再切结构更干净。之所以优先选 `80` 而不是 `88`，是因为 `88` 在 controller 口径下仍留在 0.10x 档，更多只是 exact-cost 微调；而 `80` 是第一档能把 rounded cost 压到 0.09x、同时门槛仍很宽的 probe。之所以不直接跳到 `64` 或 `72`，是因为当前主线虽在改善，但距离目标仍远，先用更稳健的第一档 width 压缩拿到真实 knee 信号，比更激进地下压更有信息价值。主要风险是 96 已经接近最小可用 local width，导致 exceed 回弹过大；但即使如此，这轮也会清楚回答当前 PK 主线的宽度 knee 是否已经到顶。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"80"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["当前真实 compatible frontier 已更新为 r261 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`：controller objective≈0.283066 = cost 0.10x + exceed 0.183066；exact round-summary objective=0.284628，曲线 `curve_still_improving=true`。","本地 exact 成本复核：`product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=1024 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80` 的 selection_accesses=229376、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=393216、exact total_cost_ratio=0.09375；controller 两位小数口径下为 0.09x。","门槛复核：若要刷新 r261 的 controller frontier，只需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1930657422542572`；若要同时刷新 r261 的 exact objective=0.284628，则需 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1908785`。","本地 allowlist 自检通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'LATENTS_PER_EXPERT', value:'80'}], fallback_architecture='product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表。","在 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` 下，候选 width 的本地 exact combined_ratio 分别为：`88 -> 0.10x`、`80 -> 0.09x`、`72 -> 0.09x`、`64 -> 0.09x`；因此 `80` 是第一档能下一个 controller cost band、同时比更激进宽度更稳健的 probe。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80` 继续刷新 controller 与 exact objective，则说明当前 PK 主线的真实 width knee 低于 96；下一轮可继续留在同 family，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=72`，确认 width 压缩还能走多远。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80` 在 controller 口径下略优但 exact objective 持平或略差，则说明 80 已接近当前 1024-bank 配方的边际 knee；下一轮不应继续线性下压到更窄宽度，而应切回新的 matched-objective architecture probe。","如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=80` 让 exceed 明显回弹、objective 不再下降，则说明当前 PK 主线在 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` 下的最小可用 local width 更接近 96；后续应停止继续扫 width，转而优先选择能明确解释 small-K exceed 更慢退化的新结构槽位。"],"reference_round":261}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0262.stdout.log:756:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d {b_{e,i}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0cE_pk(x) \u7531\u4e24\u8def product-key router \u7ed9\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cS_e^\u03c4(x) \u7531 expert \u5185 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8\u7a00\u758f\u652f\u6301\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cleft/right product-key \u6253\u5206 -> \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u50cf `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u8fd9\u7c7b\u5e26 shared/trunk \u7684\u5bb6\u65cf\u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u8fd9\u7c7b sample/batch-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e8e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u771f\u5b9e compatible incumbent \u4e0d\u662f\u63d0\u793a\u91cc\u7684\u65e7 `expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u800c\u662f r251 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u5176 controller frontier objective\u22480.293524=0.10x+0.193524\uff0cexact round-summary objective=0.290692=0.097168x+0.193524\uff0c\u4e14\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f2\u7ebf `curve_still_improving=true`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u4ecd\u6709\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u672a\u9a8c\u8bc1\u5047\u8bbe\uff0c\u4e0d\u5c5e\u4e8e\u5e94\u7acb\u5373\u5207\u69fd\u7684\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u5c40\u90e8\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u76f8\u5bf9 r251 \u53ea\u628a `NUM_EXPERTS` \u4ece 512 \u63d0\u5230 1024\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`K=32`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=96`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684 mainline \u5bb9\u91cf\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u5df2\u627e\u5230\u7684\u7a84 micro-expert knee \u4e0a\uff0c\u66f4\u5927\u7684 compositional bank \u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u80fd\u4ee5\u51e0\u4e4e\u4e0d\u53d8\u7684 rounded cost \u6362\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u591a\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\uff0c`NUM_EXPERTS=1024` \u65f6 `left_keys=32,right_keys=32`\uff0cselection_accesses=262144\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=425984\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.1015625\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u9884\u7b97\uff1bcontroller \u4e24\u4f4d\u5c0f\u6570\u53e3\u5f84\u4e0b\u4ecd\u8bb0\u4e3a 0.10x\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 controller frontier \u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1935243308544159`\uff0c\u800c\u82e5\u8981\u540c\u65f6\u5237\u65b0 r251 \u7684 exact objective\uff0c\u5219\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.1891295`\u3002r252 \u5df2\u7ecf\u8bc1\u660e\u5728\u540c\u6837 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=96` \u4e0b\u628a bank \u964d\u5230 256 \u4f1a\u8ba9 exceed \u6076\u5316\u5230 0.209794\uff1b\u4e0e\u6b64\u540c\u65f6\uff0cr248 \u4e5f\u8bc1\u660e\u5728\u66f4\u5bbd `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` \u4e0b\u628a bank \u63d0\u5230 1024 \u7684\u786e\u80fd\u6362\u56de\u66f4\u4f4e exceed\u3002\u56e0\u6b64 `1024 @ width=96` \u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u9644\u8fd1\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u6700\u5927\u3001\u4e14\u5c1a\u672a\u5728\u5f53\u524d knee \u4e0a\u88ab\u9a8c\u8bc1\u7684\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u5bb9\u91cf probe\u3002",
