research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2404:research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:72:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u7559\u5728 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e0a\u8865 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.5` \u6216\u518d\u626b\u522b\u7684\u5c40\u90e8\u8f74\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r201/r205/r206 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5f62\u6210\u8db3\u591f\u6e05\u695a\u7684\u95ed\u73af\uff1a\u66f4\u591a cleanup \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u5dee\uff0c\u66f4\u5f3a coarse \u9884\u7b97\u867d\u66f4\u597d\u4f46\u4e5f\u53ea\u628a objective \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4ecd\u672a\u8fdb\u5165\u65b0\u7684 regime\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u4e4b\u4e0b\uff0c`lowrank_expert_topk K=64 A=2 L=160 TR=16` \u4ecd\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u8865\u7684\u4e00\u6761 matched lane\uff1a\u5b83\u6709\u66f4\u4f4e exact cost\uff08\u7ea6 0.20x\uff09\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14 family \u7684\u5df2\u6709 current-target \u4fe1\u53f7\u6ca1\u6709\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a exact recipe \u4e0a\u88ab\u76f4\u63a5\u9a8c\u8bc1\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4\u53e6\u4e00\u6761\u53ef\u9009\u7684\u65b0\u69fd\u4f4d `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u5b83\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d 0.18x-0.22x \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u5df2\u5728\u7ea6 0.23x\uff0c\u8fdb\u5165\u8fd9\u8f6e\u524d\u5c31\u5df2\u7ecf\u66f4\u8d35\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 exceed \u4e5f\u7ef4\u6301\u5728 0.188 \u5de6\u53f3\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u53ea\u80fd\u505a\u5230\u63a5\u8fd1\u4f46\u96be\u4ee5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent\uff1b\u4f46\u5373\u4f7f\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e5f\u80fd\u66f4\u660e\u786e\u5730\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d low-cost \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u91cc\u201ctrunk+expert vs coarse+cleanup\u201d\u8c01\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family \u5185\u90e8\u6d88\u8017\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2594:research/history/round_summaries/round_0218.json:38:      "\u672c\u5730 smoke \u5df2\u901a\u8fc7\uff1a`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5728 `K=32, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4e0b\u53ef\u6210\u529f instantiate\u3001forward\u3001backward\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2672:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2782:research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2783:research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:37:      "已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0268.stdout.log:2864:research/history/round_summaries/round_0144.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i 是 shared low-rank coarse stage 的重构，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”是否能在约 0.30x total_cost 下优于当前刚形成的新 lowrank+expert 低成本锚点。",
