research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6668:research/history/round_summaries/round_0276.json:80:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u9636\u6bb5\u7ea6\u675f\u3002\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e r274-r275 \u90fd\u505c\u7559\u5728\u540c\u4e00 dual-shared family \u5185\uff0c\u4e14 objective \u4ecd\u672a\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent\uff1b\u6309\u7b56\u7565\u6b64\u65f6\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865 `STAGE1_RATIO` \u8fd1\u90bb\u70b9\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `dual_shared_adaptive_active_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 dual-shared \u4e0a\u505a `0.125/0.375` \u5206\u88c2\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u65b9\u5411\u201cvariable-active path by difficulty\u201d\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u5b8c\u5168\u5efa\u7acb\u5728\u5df2\u6709 winning scaffold \u7684\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u5347\u7ea7\u4e0a\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u4ec5\u65b0\u589e\u6700\u5c0f family\uff0c\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001override allowlist\u3001compatibility registry \u4e0e exact-string smoke\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f adaptive active \u5728\u5355-shared \u7248\u672c\u4e0a\u66fe\u7ed9\u8fc7\u5f31\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1b\u4f46 dual-shared scaffold \u5df2\u628a coarse \u4e3b\u5e72\u62ac\u5f3a\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u6b63\u662f\u8fd9\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 difficulty-aware cleanup \u771f\u6b63\u53d1\u6325\u4f5c\u7528\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6718:research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6753:research/history/round_summaries/round_0220.json:35:      "r218 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5f97\u5230 objective=0.437249\u3001cost=0.214844\u3001exceed=0.222406\uff1br219 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` \u5f97\u5230 objective=0.435236\u3001cost=0.214844\u3001exceed=0.220392\u3002shared-lowrank \u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0b\u5df2\u7ecf\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6868:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0286.stdout.log:6869:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然当前阶段强调 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近两轮已经连续否定 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，用一个仍留在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内、且真正改变“shared 主干 vs residual cleanup”分工关系的结构槽位做 probe，信息增量高于继续在线性 `K/LATENTS` 轴上补点。选择 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，是因为它更贴合本轮新增提示里“先用极便宜 shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的结构假设。主要风险是该 family 属于已被部分下调优先级的 shared-lowrank/two-stage 类别；但它是当前仍处在低成本辅助带、且与最新策略提示最匹配的现成结构。",
