research/history/logs/agent_round_0241.stdout.log:1660:research/history/results.tsv:69:r68_1774767244	1774767244	ok	keep	0.12482442706823349	0.1606886386871338	0.6506886386871338	2064384.0	0.49	1081344.0	0.26	983040.0	0.23	192	expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0068/round0068_standard_1774766485_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k192_20260329_144132	8e8b2e1cb369b7f816b86a324e984ee7cf779348			r67 已经对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的继续扩容给出负信号，说明“更大 routed capacity + trunk”这条线当前不值得继续加码。本轮转向更干净的直接兼容 MoE-like 探针：相对 r51 只增大 `expert_topk` 的 `NUM_EXPERTS`，用不含 trunk 的 routed-only 结构回答容量收益是否仍成立。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并owrank hetero residual 在当前 target 的优先级，后续不要继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。","如果该点质量介于 r147 与 r152 之间但仍形成新的中成本解释性锚点，则记录为 shared-lowrank hetero residual 只适合作为 0.5x 附近质量对照，而不是低成本主线。"],"notes_to_memory":["r155 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` FVU=0.14630839228630066，r156 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert @ K=96` FVU=0.14623424410820007；两条 shared-lowrank 无 residual 低成本线在当前 target 上都明显落后于 0.28x-0.30x frontier。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1843200，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=2236416，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.53，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮允许把预算上移到略高于 0.5x 的质量锚点，因为当前低成本两条 shared-lowrank 探针已连续失败；当前更重要的是回答 residual cleanup 是否能挽回这条 hetero-MoE 结构线。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；本轮更重要的是利用当前 matched recipe 做一次干净的结构切换。之所以不继续沿 r155/r156 的 0.28x 线做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 微调，是因为它们已经在当前 target 上给出几乎相同的失败结果；而 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 是当前 shared-lowrank 方向里唯一还有历史正信号、且仍符合 operator hint 的 hetero-MoE+residual 候选。主要风险是 K 从 112/128 压到 96 后，该 family 可能仍被 r152 直接压制；但即使失败，也能更干净地终止一条当前仍未完全回答的结构假设。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`。这是一次针对 hetero-MoE+residual 的 matched architecture probe，用来判断 shared-lowrank 方向在加入 residual cleanup 后，是否还能形成一个值得保留的 0.5x 左右结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0241.stdout.log:1716:research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32926:research/history/logs/agent_round_0198.stdout.log:982:research/history/logs/agent_round_0191.stdout.log:3048:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(h(x))} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(r(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1a\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)` \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u79e9 coarse bottleneck\uff0c`{u_i}` \u662f shared/coarse \u5206\u652f\u7684\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`r(x)=x-x_coarse` \u8868\u793a\u7ecf\u7b2c\u4e00\u9636\u6bb5 shared/coarse \u91cd\u6784\u540e\u7684\u6b8b\u5dee\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f routed expert residual \u5b50\u5e93\u7684\u9759\u6001\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u5148\u7528\u6781\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 shared low-rank/coarse \u5206\u652f\u5403\u6389\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c\u518d\u8ba9\u5c11\u91cf routed experts \u53ea\u505a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b50\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201cshared/coarse \u67e5\u8868 + routed residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d frontier\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u989d\u5916\u63d0\u793a\u5df2\u628a\u95ee\u9898\u6536\u675f\u5230\u201c\u4fdd\u6301 very short active path\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u589e\u5927\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u5e76\u8ba9 shared/coarse branch \u8d1f\u8d23\u4e3b\u5e72\u3001routed experts \u53ea\u505a sparse residual cleanup\u201d\uff1b\u5728\u5df2\u77e5 `expert_topk` \u4e0e `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` \u90fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u65b0\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u95ee\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family \u8865 `K/LATENTS`\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7528\u4e00\u4e2a\u771f\u6b63\u6539\u53d8\u2018\u5bb9\u91cf\u4e0e\u6fc0\u6d3b\u8def\u5f84\u5173\u7cfb\u2019\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u505a matched architecture probe\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r165 \u53ea\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=108`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201ccheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup\u201d\u662f\u5426\u6bd4\u8fd1\u671f\u5931\u8d25\u7684 routed-only / fully-factorized \u65b9\u5411\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d low-cost anchors\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u4e0b selection_accesses=647168\u3001deployment_accesses=442368\u3001combined_accesses=1089536\uff0c\u5bf9\u5e94 combined_ratio \u7ea6 `0.26x`\uff0c\u7565\u9ad8\u4e8e\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u4e0a\u6cbf\u4f46\u660e\u786e\u5904\u4e8e\u5141\u8bb8\u7684 `0.25x-0.35x` \u8f85\u52a9\u5e26\u5185\uff0c\u4e5f\u663e\u8457\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
