research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:1998:research/history/logs/agent_round_0189.stdout.log:358:179:r178_1774880994	1774880994	ok	discard	0.15794138610363007	108	shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0178/round0178_standard_1774880509_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k108_20260330_222156	f7d2f70e0d8346de0e9d928e2369a61bcf379bde			以 r165 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，做一轮 `0.26x` 左右的辅助带 architecture probe。目标是直接回答：在当前 low-cost anchor recipe 下，把 shared 分支改成更轻的 low-rank bottleneck、同时保留 expert-specific full heads，是否比 routed-only 或 fully-factorized 方向更值得继续。	这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然该点略高于 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近三轮已经连续排除了 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，当前最需要的是用一个仍在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内的高优先级结构槽位，把“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”这条线做一次更干净的 matched validation。选择它而不是继续回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 或 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，是因为前者已有更强负信号，后者又属于当前已明确下调优先级的 two-stage/hetero residual 方向。主要风险是该 family 在 r172/r174 已有偏弱结果；但这次是以当前更相关的 r165 low-cost anchor recipe 做 fresh matched probe，结论会更直接。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0178_standard_1774880509.log
