research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33002:research/history/logs/agent_round_0144.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i 是 shared low-rank coarse stage 的重构，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”是否能在约 0.30x total_cost 下优于当前刚形成的新 lowrank+expert 低成本锚点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.30x 下明显优于 r143，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，继续定位 coarse/residual 的低成本分工边界。","如果结果只与 r143 接近，则说明把 trunk 从全局 lowrank 改成 shared low-rank coarse stage 的结构收益有限，后续可优先转向带全局 residual 的三段式结构，而不是继续打磨这条两段式线。","如果新 family 明显劣于 r143，则可以更明确地把当前 low-cost 主线保留在 `lowrank_expert_topk`，同时下调 shared-lowrank two-stage 方向优先级。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，真实改动仅在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","按 `sae-architecture-integration` 做了 exact architecture smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 已可 instantiate/forward/backward。","成本自检：selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":143,"self_review":"这轮满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r143 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 刚形成新低成本 anchor 之后，继续在其内部做局部扫参会过早收缩搜索空间；新增一个最小可运行的两段式原型 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，更符合当前阶段对“shared experts + routed experts / two-stage residual expert”结构槽位的补证据需求。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是用 shared low-rank coarse stage 替代 full lowrank trunk 可能损失一部分全局主干表达，但这正是本轮要验证的结构问题。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`：用 shared low-rank coarse stage 先做第一段重构，再让 expert residual stage 处理剩余结构。建议本轮以 r143 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，直接测试这条新的两段式 hetero MoE 结构能否在约 0.30x total_cost 下形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
